#ROOM
Vnum     21000
Name     &GThe Broken Archway of Dire Maul&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The humid air of the Feralas jungle is left behind as you 
step into the shadow of the massive elven ruins. A high, 
crumbling archway marks the entrance to the once-great city of 
Eldre'Thalas. The air here hums with the residue of thousands 
of years of arcane experimentation.
~
Exit
Direction out~
ToRoom    37040
Desc      Return to the Feralas jungle.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    21001
Desc      The path to the Warpwood Quarter.~
