#ROOM
Vnum     21001
Name     &gThe Warpwood Quarter - Entrance&d~
Sector   forest~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Nature has reclaimed this section of the city with a 
vengeance. Thorny vines and massive trees burst through 
the marble floors, and a thick green mist clings to the 
ground. The sound of high-pitched giggling can be heard 
from the shadows.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    21000
Desc      The main archway.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    21002
Desc      The overgrown garden.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21100 1 21001
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21002
Name     &gThe Overgrown Garden&d~
Sector   forest~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, circular courtyard filled with gnarled trees and 
blooming, multi-colored flowers. Warpwood lashers move through 
the undergrowth, their thorns dripping with a paralytic sap.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    21001
Desc      The quarter entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    21003
Desc      The Satyr's Sanctuary.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21109 10 21002
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21003
Name     &mThe Satyr's Sanctuary - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The greenery gives way to stone halls decorated with 
vile demonic runes. The air smells of sulfur and old 
blood. Vile-tongue tricksters lurk behind the pillars, 
waiting for prey.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    21002
Desc      The overgrown garden.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    21004
Desc      Deep into the sanctuary.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21116 5 21003
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21004
Name     &mThe Satyr's Sanctuary - Heart&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the demonic presence in the East wing. A 
large, blackened altar sits in the center of the room, 
pulsing with shadow energy. Lord Vyletongue can sometimes 
be seen here conferring with his lieutenants.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    21003
Desc      The sanctuary entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    21005
Desc      Toward Alzzin's Lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21120 5 21004
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21005
Name     &gThe Lair of Alzzin the Wildshaper&d~
Sector   forest~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The deepest part of the Warpwood Quarter. A massive tree, 
twisted into a grotesque shape, dominates the center 
of the cavern. Alzzin stands before the tree, his 
hands glowing with dark green magic as he continues 
to corrupt the forest spirits.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    21004
Desc      The satyr heart.~
