#ROOM
Vnum     21030
Name     &BThe Capital Gardens - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here is thick with arcane static. White marble 
halls stretch out into the dark, and a ghostly blue 
light emanates from the walls. Highborne spirits 
wander these halls in a permanent trance.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    21000
Desc      The main archway.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    21031
Desc      The Hall of the Highborne.~
