#ROOM
Vnum     21031
Name     &BThe Hall of the Highborne&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide thoroughfare built for elven parades. Elegant 
statues of ancient queens line the walls, though many 
have been defaced. Arcane aberrations float through 
the hall, looking for mana to consume.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    21030
Desc      The gardens entrance.~
