Vnum     21032
Name     &BThe Athenaeum - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive library filled with thousands of ancient scrolls 
and books. Many are written in a dialect of Darnassian 
that has not been spoken in millennia. Spectral 
librarians carefully tend to the shelves.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    21031
Desc      The Highborne hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
