Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The quietest part of the city. Tables and chairs of 
petrified wood are scattered through the room. Magister 
Kalendris stands near a high window, gazing out at the 
ruins with unblinking eyes.
~
Exit
Direction south~
