Name     &mThe Prison of Immol'thar - Perimeter&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A series of high stone balconies overlooking a massive 
central pit. Five large pylons pulse with a sickly 
purple light, focusing their energy into the center 
of the room. Shen'dralar zealots stand guard at each pylon.
~
