Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A lavishly decorated room at the back of the prison. 
Prince Tortheldrin sits upon a throne of white marble, 
his armor tarnished and his mind far away. He 
grips his sword with trembling hands, ready to 
kill anyone who threatens his immortality.
~
