Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here is crude and heavy, reflecting the 
ogres who now occupy this quarter. Spiked wooden walls 
and piles of trash litter the once-elegant streets. 
Gordok reavers patrol the entry in pairs.
~
